        "workflow: rg -n \"File Size Limits|LOC|line count\" Makefile scripts docs/guides/ci-strategy.md :: no active line-count enforcement gate found"
      ],
      "plan": [
        "Implement a deterministic file-size check script with configurable ignore list for generated/vendor paths.",
        "Wire the check into local CI entrypoints (`make ci-fast`/`make agent-ci` tier policy as appropriate).",
        "Document enforcement behavior and remediation guidance in CI strategy docs.",
        "Add regression tests for the size-check script behavior (pass/fail paths).",
        "Verify by running `make ci-fast` and confirming the new guard reports current offenders until split tasks are completed."
